Package: pepdiff
Type: Package
Title: Workflows for Characterising and Analysing Peptide Quantifications
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Dan MacLean
Maintainer: Dan MacLean <dan.maclean@tsl.ac.uk>
Description: Provides functions for developing workflows to characterise, evaluate 
    and perfom differential abundance analysis in tabular data from quantified Mass Spec
    experiments. Typically used for experiments with Gene, Peptide, Time, Genotype, 
    Biorep, Techrep and Quantification variables.
